name: Brandi Muchler
text: this is by far my favorite pizza hut restaurant. the staff are the friendly and so nice. they actually care and ask you questions come back and check on you and make sure everything is done to PERFECTION and in a timely manor. ill travel outta my way just for this location!   GREAT JOBS GUYS!

text: I have never been to a city where Pizza Hut DID NOT DELIVER!
